2000年，魔鬼魚隊退休了博格斯的12號球衣。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.baseball-almanac.com/feats/feats10.shtml|title=Retired Uniform Numbers in the American League|access-date=July 25, 2008|work=Baseball Almanac.com|archive-date=2007-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070429152947/http://www.baseball-almanac.com/feats/feats10.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>2004年，他成功入選紅襪隊名人堂，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://boston.redsox.mlb.com/bos/history/feature_hall_of_fame.jsp|title=Red Sox Hall of Fame|access-date=July 25, 2008|work=RedSox.com|archive-date=2011-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111016124327/http://boston.redsox.mlb.com/bos/history/feature_hall_of_fame.jsp|dead-url=no}}</ref>並在2016年獲得紅襪隊退休26號球衣。<ref>{{cite tweet|user=RedSox|author=Red Sox|number=679018362828099584|date=21 December 2015|title=Wade Boggs' #RedSox uniform number 26 will be retired this May!}}</ref>
